   White House Addresses

   The mailing addresses for business mail to White House staff located in
   the buildings within the White House complex are as follows:

   The White House
   Washington, DC 20502

   The Eisenhower Office Building
   1600 Pennsylvania Avenue, NW.
   Washington, DC 20503

   New Executive Office Building
   725 17^th Street NW.
   Washington, DC 20503

   Letters sent to any of these addresses should also include the name and
   room number of the addressee.

